SpNote.note: Each MSB contains just a target component. The MSB title gives the HIP star name, RA (hh:mm), Dec (dd), V magnitude and Spectral Type. Stars were selected from the Hipparcos catalogue, excluding Dec >+60 and Dec < -30. Stars with "n", "s" and "m" spectral subclasses were excluded.
